# Privacy Policy for Grocery

Your Privacy Matters to Us

We value your privacy and want to ensure you have a clear understanding of how we handle your data when you use our app, Grocery. This Privacy Policy explains our commitment to protecting your information.
Data Collection

Grocery is designed to provide a seamless experience with Amazon Alexa. In order to do this, we need access to your Amazon Alexa lists. To enable this functionality, our servers require your specific Alexa-UserId. Please be assured that both the server and your data are under our strict control and cannot be accessed by any unauthorized parties.

### Data Protection
We take your data security seriously. Rest assured that Grocery collects no data or personal information other than what is necessary to enable its core functionality with Amazon Alexa. Your privacy is of utmost importance to us.

### Contact Us
If you have any questions or suggestions regarding this Privacy Policy, please do not hesitate to reach out to us via email at grocery+development.eggers@gmail.com. Your feedback is important to us, and we are here to address any concerns you may have.

### Updates to Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy periodically to reflect any changes in our data handling practices or legal requirements. We encourage you to review this page regularly for any updates. We will notify you of any changes by posting the revised Privacy Policy on this page, and these changes will become effective immediately upon posting.

Thank you for trusting Grocery with your data and for using our app. Your privacy is our priority, and we are committed to maintaining the highest standards of data protection.
